value.title: Bay Area BioPharma Networking Hikes
value.description:
About Event

​Explore restored wetland and shoreline bird habitat along the bay in San Francisco's southeast while networking.

Bring binoculars, if you have them, to better view shorebirds during low tide.

​After the hike (~1:30pm), we can head into the Bayview to find some snacks/drinks.

​RSVP to access the event chat ('speech bubble icon' in lower right corner) and/or join the WhatsApp to get the networking started early, coordinate carpools and receive hike updates.

When: Sat January 10th
